> A foundational C library written from scratch.

## 📝 Goal

Recreate many of the standard C library functions, such as:

- `ft_strlen`
- `ft_strcpy`
- `ft_memcpy`
- `ft_atoi`
- `ft_split`

…and many others!

## 🧠 Skills

- Pointer arithmetic
- Memory management (heap vs. stack)
- Buffer safety
- Header file structure

